message.body: Hi ##### I am coming to philly this weekend. Will you be around?
That's good to hear. I don't know if I will be able to hang out because I'm broke and not feeling well. But maybe I can meet up for a drink. What are you going to be in town for?
Oh no, are you okay? I am just coming to hang with friends. Jason and I separated so just feeling like being with friends.

Yeah I'm I in the same boat, ######### about ############with ### and have a ##### from my horrible new housemate who ################################ right below my room. I just need a ####### and am low on funds but we should meet up and try to be happy about the world
Sounds good :) let's plan to hang on Friday or Saturday if you can--naz and I are going to the Barnes in Saturday if you want to come otherwise let's hang on Friday.
It sounds like a good idea. Let me know your schedule as Friday approaches. Take care.
